snippet.title: Demons Happened - Introless trailer
snippet.description:
Whishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1992020/Demons_Happened/

Play as a ghost as dead on the inside as he is on the outside in Demons Happened, a top down shooter where you'll fight demons with demons on a journey to fix your tv.

New version of the trailer, without the intro dialogue to see if I get better engagement.

Follow https://twitter.com/DelusionalScrap for updates!
Coming to Steam in Summer 2022.


Trailer soundtrack: By Kevin MacLeod, incompetech.com, licensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 4.0 License (http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)
